cms-medicare-savings-programs.title: Medicare Savings Programs (MSP)
cms-medicare-savings-programs.headline: Medicare Savings Programs (MSP)
cms-medicare-savings-programs.summary: Get help paying your Medicare premiums. If you meet certain conditions, Medicare Savings Programs may alos pay Medicare insurance deductibles, coinsurance, and copayments.
cms-medicare-savings-programs.eligibilit: You are at least 65 years old or you have a disability.
